Here it comes.

25
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:32,225
Dragon Transformation, transform!

26
00:02:32,225 --> 00:02:34,400

27
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:50,260
We've already used five groups of people as a diversion.

28
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:54,420
We're sure that they didn't catch up to us.

29
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:58,700
Is our mission considered complete, then?

30
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:03,180
If that's all there is, that means we only helped a couple get together

31
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:05,740
and annoy Prince Jingyu.

32
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:08,420
Of course, it's more than that.

33
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:14,560
Isn't this Feili, the Soul Official?

34
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:20,220
Leave the rest to us.

35
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:25,420
Esteemed envoys, we dare not trouble the two of you for such dirty deeds.

36
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:28,880
Does that mean the two of you are going to act together?

37
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,380
You guys should stop asking questions.

38
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:32,220
Instead, you should return to Tianqi as soon as possible

39
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:35,900
and continue to lie low while planning for the grand scheme.

40
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,060
Great.

41
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:43,000
But Feili, you mustn't let us down.

42
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,660
Finally, I got everything sorted.

43
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:14,980
Brother Ye, what's with all the trouble?

44
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:18,140
Isn't it better to live directly in the mountains?

45
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,820
This place is pretty good too.

46
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:27,520
Isn't it lonely to live alone?

47
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:33,360
You're a young boy. Do you understand the meaning of loneliness?

48
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,940
Brother Ye, you have some guests.

49
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:59,440
- Young Master. 
 - Why are you all back?

50
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:02,560
Young Master, we were supposed to lie low within Tianqi City

51
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:05,000
and inquire about Miss Yi under your orders.

52
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,780
But a benefactor showed up a few days ago.

53
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:09,440
He gave us access to an opportunity.

54
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:21,000
Young Master, I'll leave the two of you to it. I'll tell you the details later.

55
00:05:24,906 --> 00:05:29,346
♫  Even as the time passes quickly between spring and autumn  ♫

56
00:05:29,346 --> 00:05:35,126
♫  I will never see the face of my old friend again  ♫

57
00:05:35,126 --> 00:05:40,806
♫  Beautiful years have passed, but dreams in my heart are still unfulfilled  ♫

58
00:05:40,806 --> 00:05:46,726
♫  Love and resentment are entangled, and I'm still frozen in the past  ♫

59
00:05:49,146 --> 00:05:54,701
♫  Allow me to see you one more time before I leave  ♫

60
00:05:54,701 --> 00:06:00,301
♫  Longing, Longing for karma that won't come  ♫

61
00:06:00,301 --> 00:06:06,001
♫  Balancing on a thin line, why am I afraid to close my eyes  ♫

62
00:06:06,001 --> 00:06:07,641
♫  What I can't bear most  ♫

63
00:06:07,641 --> 00:06:11,781
♫  Is that from now on you're alone in this world  ♫

64
00:06:11,781 --> 00:06:14,881
♫  By the window  ♫

65
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,200
On the day of your wedding,

66
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:26,200
I was there.

67
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,305
I know.

68
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,455
I heard you.

69
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:34,900
I went there with your senior.

70
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:38,060
We managed to reach the mansion's entrance.

71
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:43,614
I was even inside the mansion. I gave it my all.

72
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:50,260
I've tried my best to improve my martial arts since leaving Tianqi.

73
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:56,000
This way, I can go and pick you up once I can defeat them.

74
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:59,950
♫  Hoping that my dreams will still be fulfilled  ♫

75
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:02,220
♫  Memories seep into my mind, filling it with love and longing  ♫

76
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:07,000
If I have to wait until then, will I be old?

77
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:11,374
♫  Alas, sighing at a fate that is so sorrowful  ♫

78
00:07:11,374 --> 00:07:16,980
♫  Because of you, the gratitude and grievances stir yet remain unsaid  ♫

79
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:18,865
You'll never grow old.

80
00:07:18,865 --> 00:07:22,785
